data.description: Welcome to this exceptional two-story pool home, nestled within a highly sought-after Palm Harbor neighborhood. Set on an expansive corner lot spanning almost 14,000 square feet, this residence boasts captivating curb appeal with its lush Zoysia grass and artfully landscaped surroundings, accented by privacy-enhancing bushes. The generously sized screened-in pool (14'x 33') serves as a delightful focal point.    Upon arrival, you'll be greeted by two separate driveways, each catering to the main residence and the convenient interior mother-in-law suite. The main floor beckons with an inviting open-concept design, seamlessly merging a well-appointed work-in kitchen with a spacious dining and living great room. A master suite, powder room, laundry facilities, and the self-contained in-law suite all graciously occupy the ground level. The in-law suite boasts a commodious bedroom, living room  and a well-appointed ensuite, accessible through both a private exterior entrance and an interior doorway.    Both the master and in-law suite bathrooms are thoughtfully designed for accessibility. Ascending to the second floor, you'll discover two additional bedrooms and a shared bathroom. The second bedroom is equipped with built-in desks and a convenient Murphy bed that remains with the property. Recent years have witnessed a series of impressive upgrades to the home, including a new roof in 2018, solar panels installed in 2020, a fresh hot water tank in the same year, and a comprehensive whole-house water filtration and softening system in place since 2020.    Further enhancements include a new pool pump in 2020, a fresh pool filter in 2022, and the installation of a new Lennox HVAC system complete with UV technology in the main dwelling. The master bathroom now features a roll-in shower, added in 2022. The property boasts additional amenities, including a well, a sprinkler system, and well-maintained gutters. Eagerly awaiting its new owners, this home presents an excellent canvas for personalization and transformation into a forever haven. With its abundant potential, this residence also offers the exciting possibility of generating supplementary income.
